d">256GB 型号的</a>售价为 390 美元。</p><h2> Fitbit Inspire 3 </h2><p><core-commerce id="88ef035c6d2e4d54925618779fdb27ed" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAcnXNRPU90D1tBoD9oLy_vaxDQruTnUDXTVt8RjeMJhk&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FFitbit-Management-Intensity-Tracking-Midnight%2Fdp%2FB0B5F9SZW7" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/Fitbit-Management-Intensity-Tracking-Midnight/dp/B0B5F9SZW7?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Fitbit Inspire 3</a>在多家零售商处的售价为 80 美元，比我们追踪到的最优惠价格贵了 10 美元，但仍比 Fitbit 的标价低 20 美元。 Inspire 3 凭借其轻便防水的设计、彩色触摸屏、准确的健康监测和长达 10 天的电池续航时间，成为我们 <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-fitness-trackers-133053484.html">最喜​​欢的 100 美元或以下的健身追踪器</a>。它缺少我们首选的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAf5P6caVRRlIxCAnoVbpandrM57F9a8MV5GH6zLhx4r0&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB09BXQ4HMB%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B09BXQ4HMB/ref=ox_sc_act_title_1?smid=ATVPDKIKX0DER&amp;psc=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Fitbit Charge 5</a>的集成 GPS，但它仍然提供自动锻炼检测、智能手机警报、心率监测、睡眠跟踪和血氧监测等基本功能。</p><h2>亚马逊 Fire 电视棒 4K Max </h2><p><core-commerce id="57753133af8f482189973f823819e115" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&a