jMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9BcHBsZS1NYWNCb29rLUxhcHRvcC0xMiVFMiU4MCU5MWNvcmUtMTklRTIlODAlOTFjb3JlL2RwL0IwQlNIREpHOVQ_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMXFvLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIxNTljZTU0Ni02N2M5LTRhNTYtYjVlMC1jNDcyZGU3ZmViMjIifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAdqK78wo7Dcu-x3KtXS2N7GK8sajhT5WKS9RGiRa5VQU&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MacBook-Laptop-12%25E2%2580%2591core-19%25E2%2580%2591core%2Fdp%2FB0BSHDJG9T" class="rapid-with-clickid">16.2 英寸 MacBook Pro</a>版本售价降至 2,249 美元。这当然不便宜，但它符合该配置的历史最低价，并且比苹果的建议零售价低 250 美元。</p><h2> Audible Premium Plus（3 个月） </h2><p><core-commerce id="eda20b124c8341768f0e9efee8c0f9a7" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>新加入<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:87;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9oei9hdWRpYmxlL21scC9tZW1iZXJzaGlwL3ByZW1pdW1wbHVzL21vbnRobHk_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMXFvLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIxNTljZTU0Ni02N2M5LTRhNTYtYjVlMC1jNDcyZGU3ZmViMjIifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAWJ09zaX8zgv7TyViiQK83Qev6CEbSXwbUI2PBPGns_d&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fhz%2Faudible%2Fmlp%2Fmembership%2Fpremiumplus%2Fmonthly" class="rapid-with-clickid">Audible Premium Plus</a>的 Amazon Prime 会员可以免费获得三个月的有声读物服务。通常，30 天免费试用后，会员费用为每月 14.95 美元。这项优惠从 Prime Day 之前就开始提供，但亚马逊表示该优惠将于 7 月 31 日结束，因此请将此视为公益广告。 Premium Plus 是 Audible 的<a data-i13n="cpos:88;pos:1" href="https://help.audible.com/s/article/what-is-included-in-audible-membership-plans?language=en_US">最高级别</a>：除了精选有声读物、播客和其他可按需访问的音频内容之外，它还包含每月信用额度，让您可以永久购买 Audible 商店中的任何书籍。许多人会接受更便宜的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Audible;elmt:;cpos:89;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=48d7033d-90c5-411b-a91f-91b092b1b53c&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Audible&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI0OGQ3MDMzZC05MGM1LTQxMWItYTkxZi05MWIwOTJiMWI1M2MiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYXVkaWJsZS5jb20vZXAvZnJlZXRyaWFsLXBsdXMiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjE1OWNlNTQ2LTY3YzktNGE1Ni1iNWUwLWM0NzJkZTdmZWIyMiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAfi_qUwBIn2kM5Ji_6TjisOQ_6L8eFl-Bot0tyP6GXce&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.audible.com%2Fep%2Ffreetrial-plus" class="rapid-with-clickid">Audible Plus</a>计划，但如果您倾向于快速咀嚼有声读物，那么 Premium Plus 可能是值得的。</p><h2> Bose QuietComfort 耳塞 II </h2><p><core-commerce id="d033ba982a224dc1b7b0760e914da4db" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:90;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAb4sGjBtGeRytUbm1aiMFPrJ1L3_OAPy4DdBXsMGLwTN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBose-QuietComfort-Cancelling-Personalized-Cancellation%2Fdp%2FB0B4PSQHD5" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/Bose-QuietComfort-Cancelling-Personalized-Cancellation/dp/B0B4PSQHD5?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">Bose QuietComfort Earbuds II</a>降价至 249 美元。虽然这比我们见过的绝对最低价格高出 20 美元，但比该货币对的通常汇率下降了 50 美元。去年，我们给 QuietComfort Earbuds II <a data-i13n="cpos:91;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/bose-quietcomfort-earbuds-2-review-130026306.html">的评分为 87 分</a>，目前它是我们 <a data-i13n="cpos:92;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-wireless-earbuds-120058222.html">最佳无线耳机</a>指南中最佳降噪选择。正如这一区别所表明的那样，它的主动降噪功能是我们测试过的所有耳机​​中最强、最全面的，更不用说真正的无线耳机了。它的低音前向声音应该也会令嘻哈和 EDM 粉丝满意，虽然耳机体积较大，但它们通常比其尺寸所建议的更舒适。然而，没有多点连接或无线充电支持，这对于价格来说令人失望。</p><h2> 100 美元 Apple 礼品卡 + 10 美元百思买礼品卡</h2><p><core-commerce id="d64bf5f6ed98469c9c6118a85a3aab83" data-type="product-list"></core-co